    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014runs like a dream and has clearly been well-loved. You might find a tiny bit of character here and there from normal use, but it\u2019s totally ready for many more adventures! It's the perfect fit for anyone looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
