    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a meticulously maintained example of an analog legend. This unit features a high-revving naturally aspirated flat-six paired with a precise short-throw manual gearbox. Recent service includes a full cooling system overhaul and a fresh set of high-performance Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. The suspension geometry has been optimized with adjustable coilovers for neutral handling and reduced body roll during high-lateral-G cornering. The drivetrain remains stout, with a limited-slip differential ensuring optimal power delivery out of the apex. While the finish shows minor road-going patina consistent with an enthusiast-driven vehicle, the mechanical vitals\u2014including compression and leak-down figures\u2014are exceptional. Zero bore scoring and a clean DME report. Ready for the canyon or the track.",
      "price": 38500.0,
