    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2019 Audi Q7 Premium Plus, finished in a timeless Orca Black Metallic. This vehicle has been a reliable family companion, stored in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like shine, though there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with standard highway driving. Inside, the Nougat Brown leather seats remain supple and free of tears, with only slight creasing visible on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic feature, from the Audi Virtual Cockpit to the Bose 3D Surround Sound system, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent working order; it recently passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection and received a fresh synthetic oil change. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brake pads were replaced last season. This listing includes two sets of keys, all-weather floor mats, and a complete folder of service records. This is a turn-key luxury SUV ready for its next owner.",
